# AaronBux Behavioral Onboarding V2 — Screenwise UX + Logic + Code Scaffold

## Product Direction

This onboarding is NOT a traditional robo-advisor risk questionnaire.

Core goal:
- identify investor transition state
- diagnose validation-seeking behavior
- explain investor evolution
- map users into decision systems/archetypes
- teach tradeoffs

The onboarding flow:

```txt
Current setup
→ transition pressure
→ reasoning style
→ market psychology
→ investor evolution
→ tradeoff philosophy
→ age/time horizon
→ goals
→ behavioral interpretation
→ archetype mapping
→ example system structure
```

