# SCREEN 7 — Age / Time Horizon

## Heading

```txt
Which age range are you in?
```

## Modifier Logic

| Age | Modifier |
|---|---|
| Under 25 | GA ×1.2, TO ×1.2, FT ×1.1 |
| 25–34 | FT ×1.1, GA ×1.1 |
| 35–44 | no modifier |
| 45–54 | BFO ×1.1, IP ×1.1 |
| 55+ | IP ×1.3, GD ×1.1, TO ×0.7 |

## Example Modifier Logic

```js
if (age === 'under25') {
  state.scores.GA *= 1.2;
  state.scores.TO *= 1.2;
  state.scores.FT *= 1.1;
}
```

