# Archetype Explanations

## BFO — Balanced Family Office

```txt
Intentional long-term compounding with structured diversification and controlled optimization.
```

## GD — Global Diversified

```txt
Simple globally diversified investing focused on consistency and long-term compounding.
```

## FT — Factor Tilt

```txt
Systematic optimization through research, factor exposure, and portfolio refinement.
```

## GA — Growth + Alternatives

```txt
Growth-focused investing with openness to innovation and non-traditional assets.
```

## TO — Tactical Opportunistic

```txt
Actively seeking opportunities through timing, positioning, and market responsiveness.
```

## IP — Income Preservation

```txt
Protecting capital while generating reliable long-term income and stability.
```

## ES — Effortless & Simple

```txt
Low-maintenance investing designed for simplicity and emotional ease.
```

